WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.580 --> 00:00:06.480
Uh-oh.

2
00:00:07.710 --> 00:00:13.000
Arai, you just... went down the stairs, right?

3
00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:14.350
What?

4
00:00:18.770 --> 00:00:21.300
Kobeni! Make peace signs and stand still.

5
00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:21.890
Uh...

6
00:00:28.850 --> 00:00:30.020
Oh, my.

7
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:38.150
Aki, what do you make of this?

8
00:00:38.530 --> 00:00:40.950
Must be a devil's ability.

9
00:00:42.330 --> 00:00:44.170
Kobeni, stand there.

10
00:00:54.850 --> 00:00:55.700
Huh?

11
00:00:57.050 --> 00:00:59.460
Why is there a room
 on the other side of the windows?

12
00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:20.620
Hey! We can't get out through any of the windows!

13
00:01:20.620 --> 00:01:22.460
They just loop back to the other side!

14
00:01:23.490 --> 00:01:25.070
Just as I feared, then.

15
00:01:26.260 --> 00:01:29.930
We can't leave the eighth floor.

16
00:01:40.340 --> 00:01:42.000
Let's look at our situation.

17
00:01:42.410 --> 00:01:48.630
Likely due to a devil's ability, whether we go up or down the stairs, we end up on the eighth floor again.

18
00:01:48.990 --> 00:01:51.010
For some reason, we can't use the elevator.

19
00:01:51.510 --> 00:01:54.020
We can't get out via the windows in the rooms.

20
00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:57.830
Going through the ceiling
 also leads back to the eighth floor.

21
00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:03.400
It's probably because
 Power killed that devil just now.

22
00:02:03.820 --> 00:02:06.600
It died with its ability to lock people in activated.

23
00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:07.490
That devil was—

24
00:02:07.490 --> 00:02:09.100
You said to kill it!

25
00:02:09.100 --> 00:02:09.780
Did not!

26
00:02:09.780 --> 00:02:14.040
When a devil dies, its abilities
 are deactivated, so it can't be that.

27
00:02:14.350 --> 00:02:16.790
Aki, how is the flesh piece reacting?

28
00:02:17.220 --> 00:02:18.290
Well...

29
00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:21.380
It's stopped reacting entirely.

30
00:02:21.790 --> 00:02:26.190
So it used that small devil to lure us into a trap.

31
00:02:26.190 --> 00:02:29.510
I've never seen a devil act in such a roundabout way.

32
00:02:29.510 --> 00:02:32.760
But if we stay trapped in here for long enough,

33
00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:35.900
other devil hunters will come to our aid...

34
00:02:37.650 --> 00:02:42.270
And we'll need to pray
 that they don't get trapped just like us.

35
00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:47.280
We're all going to die here.

36
00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.280
We're going to starve to death.

37
00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:52.760
Kobeni! Get a grip!

38
00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:56.450
Remember how you want to make money
 to send your brother to university!

39
00:02:56.450 --> 00:02:58.660
That was basically forced on me.

40
00:02:59.010 --> 00:03:05.170
My brother is very smart, so my parents
 had me work to get money for his education.

41
00:03:05.850 --> 00:03:10.800
It was either prostitution or devil hunting.

42
00:03:13.300 --> 00:03:17.020
I wanted to go to university too!

43
00:03:17.020 --> 00:03:21.620
B-But I'm going to die in this place!

44
00:03:26.530 --> 00:03:28.030
That face!

45
00:03:29.570 --> 00:03:31.320
You piece of shit!

46
00:03:31.670 --> 00:03:33.120
Stop laughing!

47
00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:38.500
Kobeni, devils love fear.

48
00:03:38.500 --> 00:03:41.580
If you get scared,
 you're giving them what they want.

49
00:03:41.890 --> 00:03:45.010
But I am scared!

50
00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:47.840
Thinking about something, Aki?

51
00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.470
The clock.

52
00:03:52.980 --> 00:03:55.720
It's been stuck at 8:18 this whole time.

53
00:03:55.720 --> 00:04:00.220
The clocks in all the rooms
 are stuck at the same time.

54
00:04:02.620 --> 00:04:08.270
It's possible that a devil's ability
 has stopped time on this floor.

55
00:04:08.270 --> 00:04:11.310
If that's the case, no help is likely to come.

56
00:04:14.170 --> 00:04:15.310
Awesome!

57
00:04:15.310 --> 00:04:16.990
We can sleep all we want!

58
00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:20.370
How stupid are you?!

59
00:04:20.730 --> 00:04:25.250
We might be stuck in here forever!

60
00:04:25.250 --> 00:04:28.850
We might, or we might not.

61
00:04:28.850 --> 00:04:30.130
Wake me up when you find out.

62
00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:32.450
Look at this nice bed.

63
00:04:32.450 --> 00:04:33.880
It's a waste not to sleep in it.

64
00:04:34.390 --> 00:04:37.140
Thanks for the free nap, mister devil.

65
00:04:47.380 --> 00:04:48.490
He's out...

66
00:04:52.930 --> 00:04:54.150
Denji!

67
00:04:54.450 --> 00:04:56.790
Denji, wake up already.

68
00:05:03.740 --> 00:05:06.630
What, did we escape already?

69
00:05:06.630 --> 00:05:08.670
Unfortunately, not yet.

70
00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:13.680
We did find out that we have running water and electricity.

71
00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:18.680
And we found some food that the guests
 left behind when they fled the hotel.

72
00:05:19.010 --> 00:05:22.680
But really, we're all close to our wits' ends.

73
00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:26.190
Aki keeps looking for the devil.

74
00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:30.060
I told him to rest a bit, but he won't listen.

75
00:05:30.500 --> 00:05:34.090
Arai was helping Aki at the start,

76
00:05:34.090 --> 00:05:37.570
but now he's succumbed to fear
 and is holed up in one of the rooms.

77
00:05:38.010 --> 00:05:42.580
Kobeni went a little crazy and tried to drink
 water from a toilet, so I knocked her out.

78
00:05:43.030 --> 00:05:45.200
As for the fiend girl...

79
00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:47.460
What's Power doing?

80
00:05:47.460 --> 00:05:50.710
I was bored, so I came up with a Nobel prize.

81
00:05:50.710 --> 00:05:55.460
If I invent a new Nobel prize, humans are going to prostrate themselves before me.

82
00:05:55.460 --> 00:06:00.190
And then I'll use that situation to become the prime minister!

83
00:06:00.190 --> 00:06:03.470
After all, I wish to see humans suffering.

84
00:06:03.970 --> 00:06:07.230
I'll start by raising the sales tax rate to 100%!

85
00:06:08.660 --> 00:06:09.960
She seems normal to me.

86
00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:10.480
Ah.

87
00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:12.350
Alrighty, then.

88
00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:16.230
Let's all keep an eye on Kobeni and Arai.

89
00:06:34.410 --> 00:06:37.130
Well, here goes my last cigarette.

90
00:06:37.490 --> 00:06:39.630
It's boring how calm you are.

91
00:06:40.010 --> 00:06:44.890
Aki is working hard, so I can take it easy.

92
00:06:44.890 --> 00:06:47.270
There's also the power of nicotine.

93
00:06:47.700 --> 00:06:51.020
It's nice being dependent on something.

94
00:06:51.350 --> 00:06:54.770
Who doesn't want something they can depend on in their life?

95
00:06:55.130 --> 00:06:57.280
That cigarette brand seems familiar.

96
00:07:00.580 --> 00:07:05.660
Well, I was the one who introduced Aki
 to the taste of cigarettes.

97
00:07:10.450 --> 00:07:12.170
Want a cig, Aki?

98
00:07:12.530 --> 00:07:14.420
Smoking erodes the bones.

99
00:07:14.420 --> 00:07:17.170
It helps you socialize, though.

100
00:07:17.170 --> 00:07:19.420
I don't intend to get close to anyone.

101
00:07:23.490 --> 00:07:26.120
Let me guess why you've come to the Bureau.

102
00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:28.180
To kill the Gun Devil, right?

103
00:07:29.930 --> 00:07:33.450
Every gloomy person in here came for that reason.

104
00:07:33.970 --> 00:07:37.820
This is the only place allowed to have pieces of it.

105
00:07:38.380 --> 00:07:42.070
As a devil hunter, you're not likely
 to live too long, so might as well smoke.

106
00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:44.820
I won't die that easily.

107
00:07:45.330 --> 00:07:46.700
Yeah, please don't.

108
00:07:47.190 --> 00:07:49.950
It's a huge hassle to have your partner die.

109
00:07:57.840 --> 00:07:59.070
What was that?

110
00:08:03.050 --> 00:08:07.200
It's common to get trouble
 from a dead partner's loved ones.

111
00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:10.980
She doesn't have the power to kill the devil,
 so she takes it out on me.

112
00:08:11.530 --> 00:08:16.680
Well, I tend to just think of it
 as part of a devil hunter's job.

113
00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:27.200
What did you do?

114
00:08:30.980 --> 00:08:34.710
I secretly stuck some gum to her clothes.

115
00:08:36.710 --> 00:08:37.790
What?!

116
00:08:38.130 --> 00:08:40.140
She got what she deserved.

117
00:08:40.140 --> 00:08:43.230
It's not about you. She just annoyed me.

118
00:08:43.230 --> 00:08:44.800
So I got back at her.

119
00:08:45.280 --> 00:08:46.300
Serves her right.

120
00:08:46.650 --> 00:08:50.040
She'll go on with her life without noticing the gum.

121
00:08:58.150 --> 00:09:00.650
Well, you know, my teacher once told me this.

122
00:09:00.970 --> 00:09:06.430
It's not the strongest or bravest hunters
 that the devils fear most.

123
00:09:06.430 --> 00:09:09.160
It's the crazy ones.

124
00:09:09.560 --> 00:09:12.260
So I think you'll survive for longer.

125
00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:15.580
Is that sarcasm?

126
00:09:15.580 --> 00:09:18.190
I'll take your dessert if you're not eating it.

127
00:09:21.170 --> 00:09:22.920
You can have this.

128
00:09:24.250 --> 00:09:26.230
They erode the bones.

129
00:09:26.230 --> 00:09:27.430
Really?

130
00:09:27.740 --> 00:09:31.890
Looks like we're going to be together
 for quite a while, so it'd be nice if you smoked too.

131
00:09:41.450 --> 00:09:43.280
Fine, I'll smoke one.

132
00:09:43.280 --> 00:09:46.570
And this will be the only one I smoke with you.

133
00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:51.280
Himeno, do you have any smokes left?

134
00:09:51.630 --> 00:09:54.290
Sorry. This is the last one.

135
00:09:54.650 --> 00:09:56.830
Then let me have it.

136
00:09:56.830 --> 00:09:57.920
Really?

137
00:09:58.610 --> 00:10:00.590
Okay, I guess.

138
00:10:02.420 --> 00:10:03.330
That's a kiss!

139
00:10:03.330 --> 00:10:04.010
No fair!

140
00:10:04.010 --> 00:10:05.170
An indirect kiss!

141
00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:06.620
Shut up.

142
00:10:10.170 --> 00:10:11.760
I have bad news.

143
00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:14.810
We killed a devil, right?

144
00:10:14.810 --> 00:10:16.930
The one I killed!

145
00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:20.180
It's growing bigger.

146
00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:34.160
I'm sure I killed it.

147
00:10:34.530 --> 00:10:36.510
It can't get out of the hotel.

148
00:10:36.510 --> 00:10:38.160
I've never seen such a shape.

149
00:10:38.730 --> 00:10:40.490
What devil is this?

150
00:10:41.430 --> 00:10:42.540
Humans!

151
00:10:42.540 --> 00:10:44.360
Hear me, humans.

152
00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:46.300
Hear me, foolish humans.

153
00:10:46.300 --> 00:10:48.800
I wish to negotiate a contract.

154
00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.420
It talks!

155
00:10:50.420 --> 00:10:51.430
A contract?

156
00:10:51.830 --> 00:10:55.380
Let me eat the human you call Denji.

157
00:10:55.380 --> 00:10:57.210
I don't mind if he's dead.

158
00:10:57.210 --> 00:10:58.680
Let me eat him.

159
00:10:58.680 --> 00:11:03.310
If you do, I shall let all the other
 devil hunters exit unharmed.

160
00:11:03.310 --> 00:11:05.070
Exit unharmed.

161
00:11:05.070 --> 00:11:06.820
Make the contract!

162
00:11:07.170 --> 00:11:08.250
Make the contract!

163
00:11:08.250 --> 00:11:08.820
Make the contract!

164
00:11:19.220 --> 00:11:20.410
Denji.

165
00:11:20.410 --> 00:11:21.790
Get eaten.

166
00:11:48.770 --> 00:11:50.320
Keep it down, will ya?

167
00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:53.660
Aki, can't you just have the Fox swallow it and get this over with?

168
00:11:54.450 --> 00:11:55.130
Yip.

169
00:11:57.540 --> 00:11:59.810
Seems like the Fox can't get here,

170
00:11:59.810 --> 00:12:02.150
because this space is isolated from the outside.

171
00:12:02.150 --> 00:12:05.130
Yeah, its body is all the way in Kyoto.

172
00:12:05.450 --> 00:12:08.230
Guess I'll use my Ghost then.

173
00:12:20.970 --> 00:12:21.980
Ugh!

174
00:12:21.980 --> 00:12:23.510
It got bigger.

175
00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:25.980
It's no use.

176
00:12:25.980 --> 00:12:29.230
This is not my actual body.

177
00:12:29.230 --> 00:12:31.990
My heart isn't here.

178
00:12:32.310 --> 00:12:33.990
This is the inside of my belly.

179
00:12:33.990 --> 00:12:34.070
This is the inside of my belly.

180
00:12:34.070 --> 00:12:34.150
This is the inside of my belly.

181
00:12:34.460 --> 00:12:38.240
My weak point is not on the eighth floor.

182
00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:42.250
The only way to get out alive
 is to make the contract.

183
00:12:42.250 --> 00:12:43.630
Hmph!

184
00:12:43.630 --> 00:12:47.310
It's not like you'll actually let them out after you kill me.

185
00:12:47.310 --> 00:12:48.750
You're wrong.

186
00:12:48.750 --> 00:12:52.230
It's saying "contract", right?

187
00:12:52.230 --> 00:12:56.260
When a devil uses the word "contract",
 that holds great power.

188
00:12:56.560 --> 00:13:01.770
If one side upholds their end,
 the other is also forced to.

189
00:13:02.110 --> 00:13:04.390
If they don't, they die.

190
00:13:04.390 --> 00:13:07.670
So there's no doubt
 it would let us out if we gave you to it.

191
00:13:08.280 --> 00:13:11.530
Himeno, we should kill him.

192
00:13:12.090 --> 00:13:16.030
After that's done and we're out, we can consider our options.

193
00:13:16.030 --> 00:13:18.780
Otherwise we'll all just starve to death in here.

194
00:13:19.170 --> 00:13:23.410
It's even allowed by law for hunters
 to make contracts with devils.

195
00:13:23.770 --> 00:13:26.040
We should make that contract!

196
00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:29.240
The devil wants to kill Denji.

197
00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:32.050
That means Denji's death
 would be to the devil's advantage.

198
00:13:32.570 --> 00:13:34.370
So we can't agree to it.

199
00:13:34.370 --> 00:13:35.920
I'm with Aki, then.

200
00:13:36.490 --> 00:13:37.720
Really?!

201
00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:39.440
I'm for killing him!

202
00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:40.430
For real?

203
00:13:40.430 --> 00:13:45.240
Even if I come up with a Nobel prize,
 I can't announce it unless I get out.

204
00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.890
Die for my Nobel!

205
00:13:46.890 --> 00:13:49.830
A fiend cannot form a contract with a devil.

206
00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:53.900
So if you kill Denji, the devil won't be forced to let us out.

207
00:13:54.380 --> 00:13:56.470
In any case, we're not killing him.

208
00:13:56.470 --> 00:13:58.410
We're devil hunters.

209
00:13:59.100 --> 00:14:01.160
We only kill devils.

210
00:14:01.160 --> 00:14:02.110
Tch.

211
00:14:03.910 --> 00:14:05.480
I'm bored. Let's sumo wrestle!

212
00:14:05.480 --> 00:14:07.660
I don't wanna play after you said to kill me!

213
00:14:14.540 --> 00:14:15.990
I'm hungry.

214
00:14:15.990 --> 00:14:20.180
Aki, do you actually have a plan for how to get out?

215
00:14:20.180 --> 00:14:24.680
If we trust what it says, that means we can't kill it.

216
00:14:24.990 --> 00:14:27.430
But I don't intend to kill Denji either.

217
00:14:27.850 --> 00:14:30.190
But we're going to starve unless we do something.

218
00:14:33.750 --> 00:14:36.030
If we run out of options, I'll use the sword.

219
00:14:36.030 --> 00:14:37.190
That's not an option.

220
00:14:38.830 --> 00:14:42.810
If using the sword would solve this,
 why don't you do it?

221
00:14:43.970 --> 00:14:46.830
Even if we run out of options,
 we're not using the sword.

222
00:14:47.490 --> 00:14:49.710
If we get to that point, I'm sorry, but...

223
00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:51.710
you'll have to die.

224
00:14:52.270 --> 00:14:53.960
What?

225
00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:55.710
Gone?!

226
00:14:55.710 --> 00:14:57.090
It's gone!

227
00:14:57.090 --> 00:15:00.470
All the food we left on the bed is gone!

228
00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:01.840
How?

229
00:15:07.500 --> 00:15:10.260
Did you eat all of it?!

230
00:15:10.260 --> 00:15:12.730
It wasn't me. It was Denji.

231
00:15:12.730 --> 00:15:14.870
That's an obvious lie!

232
00:15:14.870 --> 00:15:16.230
I get it!

233
00:15:16.230 --> 00:15:19.240
I finally get it!

234
00:15:19.980 --> 00:15:23.960
It's that fiend's ability that's trapping us here!

235
00:15:23.960 --> 00:15:25.620
I'm sure of it!

236
00:15:25.620 --> 00:15:26.620
Nope.

237
00:15:26.620 --> 00:15:28.280
Calm down, Kobeni!

238
00:15:28.280 --> 00:15:29.390
She's the Blood Fiend!

239
00:15:29.390 --> 00:15:31.470
You're taking a fiend's side?

240
00:15:31.470 --> 00:15:33.880
We're supposed to be devil hunters!

241
00:15:33.880 --> 00:15:37.060
Arai, you're on their side!

242
00:15:37.060 --> 00:15:39.010
You were a spy all along!

243
00:15:39.010 --> 00:15:40.260
He's a pie?

244
00:15:40.260 --> 00:15:42.680
I-I'm not on their side...

245
00:15:43.800 --> 00:15:46.260
You're definitely a spy!

246
00:15:50.980 --> 00:15:52.090
A scream?

247
00:15:52.090 --> 00:15:53.520
Himeno, run!

248
00:16:02.570 --> 00:16:06.220
Kill Denji and give me his heart!

249
00:16:06.220 --> 00:16:07.970
Give it!

250
00:16:07.970 --> 00:16:10.470
I swell with fear.

251
00:16:10.470 --> 00:16:13.270
I am fear!

252
00:16:13.270 --> 00:16:15.750
Fear more!

253
00:16:16.340 --> 00:16:17.880
Fear death!

254
00:16:18.290 --> 00:16:20.010
Fear everything!

255
00:16:20.530 --> 00:16:24.110
I'm going to kill Chainsaw.

256
00:16:24.110 --> 00:16:25.930
Me!

257
00:16:25.930 --> 00:16:28.810
The Eternity Devil!

258
00:16:34.950 --> 00:16:36.110
The floor slanted!

259
00:16:52.390 --> 00:16:55.730
Give me Denji's heart!

260
00:16:55.730 --> 00:16:56.670
Please!

261
00:16:56.670 --> 00:16:59.170
Someone please kill Denji!

262
00:16:59.170 --> 00:17:00.720
Please do it!

263
00:17:00.720 --> 00:17:02.240
This is getting bad!

264
00:17:02.240 --> 00:17:04.480
Let's feed him to the devil!

265
00:17:06.850 --> 00:17:08.300
I'll use the sword.

266
00:17:08.300 --> 00:17:10.560
You agree, right, Himeno?

267
00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:13.530
Himeno?!

268
00:17:14.710 --> 00:17:15.560
Hey, hey!

269
00:17:15.560 --> 00:17:17.750
What are you doing?

270
00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:21.070
If he uses the sword, we'll be able to get out.

271
00:17:21.500 --> 00:17:25.320
But then the contract would shave off
 a big chunk of Aki's lifespan.

272
00:17:25.970 --> 00:17:29.620
And he still has a lot of things to accomplish.

273
00:17:29.620 --> 00:17:31.990
So, I'm sorry, Denji.

274
00:17:32.950 --> 00:17:34.710
Forgive me!

275
00:17:35.040 --> 00:17:36.710
Hey! Get off me!

276
00:17:36.710 --> 00:17:38.210
Let go!

277
00:17:42.460 --> 00:17:44.460
Die!

278
00:18:10.960 --> 00:18:17.050
I agree that he's a disgusting piece of shit,
 who deserves to be stabbed,

279
00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:20.130
but he strives to kill the Gun Devil.

280
00:18:21.150 --> 00:18:24.720
I can't kill the Gun Devil on my own.

281
00:18:25.410 --> 00:18:33.310
I'd like to have every single
 devil hunter with the guts to face it.

282
00:18:34.050 --> 00:18:36.210
Even if it means I shorten my own life,

283
00:18:37.770 --> 00:18:40.060
I won't let Denji die!

284
00:18:41.570 --> 00:18:42.060
Power!

285
00:18:42.490 --> 00:18:44.070
You're the Blood Fiend, right?

286
00:18:44.410 --> 00:18:46.570
Can you stop his bleeding?

287
00:18:46.860 --> 00:18:50.530
I can only freely command my own blood.

288
00:18:50.530 --> 00:18:52.570
Manipulating another's is difficult.

289
00:18:54.580 --> 00:18:58.830
But if Topknot dies, there will be
 no human to make me meals.

290
00:18:59.140 --> 00:19:01.580
I suppose I can do something.

291
00:19:07.870 --> 00:19:09.220
What do I do?

292
00:19:09.640 --> 00:19:11.220
What do I do?!

293
00:19:11.220 --> 00:19:13.770
Aki! Aki! Aki!

294
00:19:13.770 --> 00:19:14.850
What do I do?!

295
00:19:15.240 --> 00:19:18.110
I-It's not my fault!

296
00:19:18.110 --> 00:19:19.100
It's you!

297
00:19:19.100 --> 00:19:21.110
It's all your fault!

298
00:19:21.110 --> 00:19:25.170
If only you'd just quietly gotten eaten,
 everything would have been fine!

299
00:19:26.340 --> 00:19:27.980
Okay, fine then!

300
00:19:27.980 --> 00:19:30.850
I'll go get eaten then.

301
00:19:30.850 --> 00:19:33.240
I'm so relieved.

302
00:19:33.930 --> 00:19:36.500
But I'm not going quietly.

303
00:19:37.420 --> 00:19:41.000
If I do manage to kill the devil,

304
00:19:41.560 --> 00:19:42.500
then...

305
00:19:42.500 --> 00:19:44.590
I haven't forgotten about that kiss!

306
00:19:45.500 --> 00:19:47.750
Have you any idea of how to kill it?

307
00:19:48.260 --> 00:19:51.760
It hurts a lot, but I'll become Chainsaw.

308
00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:54.060
Ch-Chainsaw?

309
00:19:54.060 --> 00:19:59.190
I'm not sure why, but that devil seems scared of my Chainsaw.

310
00:19:59.760 --> 00:20:04.250
That's why it's telling you all to kill me
 rather than attacking me directly.

311
00:20:05.290 --> 00:20:10.240
Also, when you hit it, it seemed to feel pain.

312
00:20:11.010 --> 00:20:12.610
And that means...

313
00:20:12.610 --> 00:20:15.280
I just need to make the pain so unbearable

314
00:20:16.030 --> 00:20:18.540
that it kills itself!

315
00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:22.040
That how a devil would think!

316
00:20:25.370 --> 00:20:28.040
You protected me.

317
00:20:28.470 --> 00:20:31.170
Mind your own business, shithead.

318
00:20:31.820 --> 00:20:36.170
I'm sick of owing people stuff!

319
00:20:36.850 --> 00:20:39.500
If we get out of this, I'm calling us even!

320
00:21:16.430 --> 00:21:19.890
I've been around the world, but there's still things I've never had to see

321
00:21:20.260 --> 00:21:24.270
Things so awful and repulsive that it all would blur

322
00:21:24.270 --> 00:21:27.650
When folks get to pushin' thirty, no one wants to stay single

323
00:21:27.650 --> 00:21:31.020
Like a dog with no one to snuggle with, you're feelin' kinda lonely

324
00:21:32.570 --> 00:21:34.490
Don't even know how fast I'll go

325
00:21:34.490 --> 00:21:36.450
I'm movin' forwards even though

326
00:21:36.450 --> 00:21:39.700
I should've lost my way so many miles ago

327
00:21:40.450 --> 00:21:42.330
I'm in a place that's gone insane

328
00:21:42.330 --> 00:21:44.290
And something's been maddening my brain

329
00:21:44.290 --> 00:21:46.540
By all accounts, I should've lost it

330
00:21:47.620 --> 00:21:49.460
Our cerebral rendezvous

331
00:21:49.460 --> 00:21:51.920
Just gotta dance through our dependence

332
00:21:51.920 --> 00:21:55.670
We're all screamin', we're all laughin', that's how we live our lives

333
00:21:55.670 --> 00:21:57.220
Our cerebral rendezvous

334
00:21:57.220 --> 00:21:59.800
It's when we dance with pride and hubris

